### ðŸ“¦ `setup.py`
```python
from setuptools import setup, find_packages

setup(
    name="plotverse",
    version="0.0.1",
    packages=find_packages(),
    install_requires=[
        "pandas",
        "matplotlib",
        "seaborn"
    ],
    author="Sanju",
    description="A combined wrapper for Pandas, Matplotlib, and Seaborn.",
    url="https://github.com/sk-sanju/plotverse",
    license="MIT",
)

